\par
\ul\b #Combos# \ulnone\b0\par
\par
This character can perform different attacks into combos to damage the oppoment. The attacks for the combo can be made up of standing attacks, crouching attacks, and even aerial attacks.\par
\par
\ul\b Examples\ulnone\b0\par
\par
Combo 1: Standing Weak Punch > Standing Medium Punch > Crouching Hard Punch > Super Jump > Jump Weak Punch, Jump Medium Punch > Jump Strong Punch.\par
\par
Combo 2: Jump Weak Punch, Jump Medium Punch > Jump Strong Punch > Ninja Tool Throw\par
\par
